{"title":"夏天，在南方","authors":["上官帅"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":7,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏天，在南方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上官帅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蝈蝈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蝈蝈一叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏天就绿了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并且，能感觉到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵阵凉意！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏天的故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掐一根狗尾草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"串起翠绿的蚂蚱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，把田园风光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和美丽的夏天拎回家……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青蛙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盛夏的傍晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外面下起了瓢泼大雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只小青蛙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然跳进我家里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它两眼呆呆地凝望着我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腹部急促地起伏呼吸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像很累的样子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机灵地跑来躲雨……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一只翠绿色的小青蛙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背上有三根细细的金线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿得仿佛透明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真是美丽极了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它在屋子里跳来跳去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不时停下来蹲坐在那里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹如一架高射炮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随时准备轰击……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时外面风更大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨更急……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我赶紧关好门窗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独自回卧室休息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小青蛙在我家待了一夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帮我消灭了不少蚊子！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第二天早晨，雨停了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我打开房门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依依不舍地——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看它回到大自然中去……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}